00:30:26.650 --> 00:30:29.370
But in terms of how long we were
spending, I think it was

00:30:29.370 --> 00:30:33.860
probably half an hour for
each kind of excursion.

00:30:33.860 --> 00:30:37.390
And then we would take the boat
