sample them and tag them.

00:30:55.340 --> 00:30:58.749
WINNIE LAM: Yeah.

00:30:58.749 --> 00:30:59.730
DR. CALEB MCCLENNEN: Great.

00:30:59.730 --> 00:31:03.850
Obviously, the minimum amount
of time as best as possible.

00:31:03.850 --> 00:31:06.420
Well, let me go through a
couple more slides here.

