No.

00:38:38.490 --> 00:38:40.260
It's a cost benefit of--

00:38:40.260 --> 00:38:43.600
in order to save these species,
which are critically

00:38:43.600 --> 00:38:47.070
endangered, we need to
understand them more, we need

00:38:47.070 --> 00:38:48.840
to be protecting them, and we
need to understand if our

00:38:48.840 --> 00:38:50.030
protections are working
or not.

00:38:50.030 --> 00:38:53.100
Because so far, there's a lot
of decline in populations.

00:38:53.100 --> 00:38:56.040
