thought of that, yeah, you

00:39:07.800 --> 00:39:09.670
should touch things when
you're on recreation.

00:39:09.670 --> 00:39:12.720
We do fully believe when you're
in the ocean, you

00:39:12.720 --> 00:39:14.840
