If you take that amount of
touching and then say, all

00:39:22.540 --> 00:39:25.410
people that happen to go on a
hotel vacation in the tropics,

00:39:25.410 --> 00:39:27.260
your impact magnifies
pretty quickly.

00:39:27.260 --> 00:39:30.130
So that was a long way of
saying, no, they're

00:39:30.130 --> 00:39:33.090
